Package org.odpi.openmetadata.governanceservers.dataengineproxy.processor

Class DataEngineProxyService

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.governanceservers.dataengineproxy.processor.DataEngineProxyService
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class DataEngineProxyService extends Object implements Runnable
Class to handle periodically polling a Data Engine for changes, for those data engines that do not provide any event-based mechanism to notify on changes.
